  <Output>
    <Options>

    <MappingFragments/>
    <OutputDef>
      <Block displayName="Initial store of variables">
        <ForEach displayName="Store Main Id and type: PRODUCTOID" recordType="cmfAsset.validatedAsset.identifiers.identifier">
          <Do>
            <If>
              <expr><![CDATA[return cmfAsset.validatedAsset.identifiers.identifier.TYPE == "PRODUCTOID";]]></expr>
              <Then>
                <Execute>
                  <expr><![CDATA[return StoreString("MAINIDStrVal", cmfAsset.validatedAsset.identifiers.identifier);]]></expr>
                </Execute>
                <Execute>
                  <expr><![CDATA[return StoreString("MAINIDTYPStrVal", cmfAsset.validatedAsset.identifiers.identifier.TYPE);]]></expr>
                </Execute>
              </Then>
              <Else/>
            </If>
          </Do>
        </ForEach>
        <ForEach displayName="Store Id and type for WIBBGLOB" recordType="cmfAsset.validatedAsset.identifiers.identifier">
          <Do>
            <If>
              <expr><![CDATA[return cmfAsset.validatedAsset.identifiers.identifier.TYPE == "WIBBGLOB";]]></expr>
              <Then>
                <Execute>
                  <expr><![CDATA[return StoreString("WIBBGLBIDVal", cmfAsset.validatedAsset.identifiers.identifier);]]></expr>
                </Execute>
                <Execute>
                  <expr><![CDATA[return StoreString("WIBBGLBIDType", cmfAsset.validatedAsset.identifiers.identifier.TYPE);]]></expr>
                </Execute>
              </Then>
              <Else/>
            </If>
          </Do>
        </ForEach>
        <ForEach displayName="Store Issue Identifiers to key. XXXStrVal eg ISINStrVal" recordType="cmfAsset.validatedAsset.identifiers.identifier">
          <Do>
            <Execute>
              <expr><![CDATA[return StoreString(Strcat(cmfAsset.validatedAsset.identifiers.identifier.TYPE, "StrVal"), cmfAsset.validatedAsset.identifiers.identifier);]]></expr>
            </Execute>
          </Do>
        </ForEach>
        <ForEach displayName="Store Issuer Idntifiers" recordType="cmfAsset.validatedAsset.relatedParty.knownRelatedParty.partyIssuer">
          <Do>
            <Execute>
              <expr><![CDATA[return StoreString(cmfAsset.validatedAsset.relatedParty.knownRelatedParty.partyIssuer.PARTY_TYPE, cmfAsset.validatedAsset.relatedParty.knownRelatedParty.partyIssuer);]]></expr>
            </Execute>
          </Do>
        </ForEach>
        <ForEach displayName="Store Classification for DMB" recordType="cmfAsset.validatedAsset.classification">
          <comment><![CDATA[EG-10523]]></comment>
          <Do>
            <If displayName="SCHEME is ProductMaster Bond Classification">
              <expr><![CDATA[return Strcmp(cmfAsset.validatedAsset.classification.SCHEME, "ProductMaster Bond Classification");]]></expr>
              <Then>
                <Execute>
                  <expr><![CDATA[return StoreString(cmfAsset.validatedAsset.classification, cmfAsset.validatedAsset.classification);]]></expr>
                </Execute>
              </Then>
              <Else/>
            </If>
          </Do>
        </ForEach>
        <Execute disabled="1" displayName=":MTN">
          <expr><![CDATA[if (Strcmp(cmfAsset.validatedAsset.assetName.SUBTYPE, "MTN"))
	return StoreString("BONDTYP2", "MTNNOTE_");
else
	return StoreString("BONDTYP2", "NONMTNNOTE_");]]></expr>
        </Execute>
        <Execute displayName="Maturity Date">
          <expr><![CDATA[if (FieldPresent(cmfAsset.validatedAsset.assetName.MATURITY_DATE))
	return StoreString("MatDateVal", cmfAsset.validatedAsset.assetName.MATURITY_DATE);
else
	return "";]]></expr>
        </Execute>
        <Execute displayName="store IssueCurrencyVal">
          <expr><![CDATA[if (FieldPresent(cmfAsset.validatedAsset.assetName.ISSUE_CURRENCY))
	return StoreString("IssueCurrencyVal", cmfAsset.validatedAsset.assetName.ISSUE_CURRENCY);
else
	return "";]]></expr>
        </Execute>
        <Execute displayName="store MIN_TRADABLE_QTY">
          <expr><![CDATA[if (FieldPresent(cmfAsset.validatedAsset.incomeDetail.MIN_TRADABLE_QTY))
	return StoreString("MIN_TRADABLE_QTY", cmfAsset.validatedAsset.incomeDetail.MIN_TRADABLE_QTY);
else
	return "";]]></expr>
        </Execute>
        <Execute displayName="Coupon Currency">
          <expr><![CDATA[if (FieldPresent(cmfAsset.validatedAsset.incomeDetail.couponDetail.couponTerm.COUPON_CURRENCY))
	return StoreString("CouponCurrencyVal", cmfAsset.validatedAsset.incomeDetail.couponDetail.couponTerm.COUPON_CURRENCY);
else
	return "";]]></expr>
        </Execute>
        <Execute displayName="DISPLAY_COUPON_PERCENTAGE">
          <expr><![CDATA[if (FieldPresent(cmfAsset.validatedAsset.incomeDetail.couponDetail.DISPLAY_COUPON_PERCENTAGE))
	return StoreString("DISPLAY_COUPON_PERCENTAGE", cmfAsset.validatedAsset.incomeDetail.couponDetail.DISPLAY_COUPON_PERCENTAGE);
else
	return "";]]></expr>
        </Execute>
        <Execute displayName="COUPON_TYPE">
          <expr><![CDATA[return StoreStringIf("COUPON_TYPE", cmfAsset.validatedAsset.incomeDetail.couponDetail.COUPON_TYPE, OneHasValue(cmfAsset.validatedAsset.incomeDetail.couponDetail.COUPON_TYPE));]]></expr>
        </Execute>
        <Execute displayName="COUPON_TYPE_RESET_DATE">
          <expr><![CDATA[return StoreStringIf("COUPON_TYPE_RESET_DATE", cmfAsset.validatedAsset.incomeDetail.couponDetail.COUPON_TYPE_RESET_DATE, FieldPresent(cmfAsset.validatedAsset.incomeDetail.couponDetail.COUPON_TYPE_RESET_DATE));]]></expr>
        </Execute>
        <Execute displayName="COUPON_TERM_START_DATE">
          <expr><![CDATA[return StoreStringIf("COUPON_TERM_START_DATE", cmfAsset.validatedAsset.incomeDetail.couponDetail.couponTerm.COUPON_TERM_START_DATE, OneHasValue(cmfAsset.validatedAsset.incomeDetail.couponDetail.couponTerm.COUPON_TERM_START_DATE));]]></expr>

        <Execute displayName="EOM_CONVENTION">
          <expr><![CDATA[return StoreStringIf("EOM_CONVENTION", cmfAsset.validatedAsset.incomeDetail.couponDetail.couponPayment.EOM_CONVENTION, FieldPresent(cmfAsset.validatedAsset.incomeDetail.couponDetail.couponPayment.EOM_CONVENTION));]]></expr>
        </Execute>
        <Execute displayName="FIXED_RATE">
          <expr><![CDATA[return StoreStringIf("FIXED_RATE", cmfAsset.validatedAsset.incomeDetail.couponDetail.couponTerm.FIXED_RATE, OneHasValue(cmfAsset.validatedAsset.incomeDetail.couponDetail.couponTerm.FIXED_RATE));]]></expr>

        <Execute displayName="EX_DIV_DAYS">

        </Execute>
        <Execute displayName="EX_DATE_CALENDAR">
          <expr><![CDATA[return StoreStringIf("EX_DATE_CALENDAR", cmfAsset.validatedAsset.incomeDetail.couponDetail.couponPayment.EX_DATE_CALENDAR, FieldPresent(cmfAsset.validatedAsset.incomeDetail.couponDetail.couponPayment.EX_DATE_CALENDAR));]]></expr>

        <Execute displayName="FIRST_COUPN_PAY_DATE">
          <expr><![CDATA[return StoreStringIf("FIRST_COUPON_PAY_DATE", cmfAsset.validatedAsset.incomeDetail.couponDetail.FIRST_COUPON_PAY_DATE, OneHasValue(cmfAsset.validatedAsset.incomeDetail.couponDetail.FIRST_COUPON_PAY_DATE));]]></expr>
        </Execute>
        <Execute displayName="FIRST_ACCRUAL_START_DATE">
          <expr><![CDATA[return StoreStringIf("FIRST_ACCRUAL_START_DATE", cmfAsset.validatedAsset.incomeDetail.couponDetail.FIRST_ACCRUAL_START_DATE, OneHasValue(cmfAsset.validatedAsset.incomeDetail.couponDetail.FIRST_ACCRUAL_START_DATE));]]></expr>
        </Execute>
        <Execute displayName="CPI_INDEX_RATIO">
          <expr><![CDATA[return StoreStringIf("CPI_INDEX_RATIO", cmfAsset.validatedAsset.principalDetail.CPI_INDEX_RATIO, OneHasValue(cmfAsset.validatedAsset.principalDetail.CPI_INDEX_RATIO));]]></expr>
        </Execute>
        <Execute displayName="SINKING_FUND">
          <expr><![CDATA[return StoreStringIf("SINKING_FUND", cmfAsset.validatedAsset.principalDetail.SINKING_FUND, OneHasValue(cmfAsset.validatedAsset.principalDetail.SINKING_FUND));]]></expr>
        </Execute>
        <Execute displayName="PAYMENT_DATE_FREQ_DAY">
          <expr><![CDATA[return StoreStringIf("PAYMENT_DATE_FREQ_DAY", cmfAsset.validatedAsset.incomeDetail.couponDetail.couponPayment.PAYMENT_DATE_FREQ_DAY, OneHasValue(cmfAsset.validatedAsset.incomeDetail.couponDetail.couponPayment.PAYMENT_DATE_FREQ_DAY));]]></expr>
        </Execute>
        <Execute displayName="PERPETUAL">
          <expr><![CDATA[return StoreStringIf("PERPETUAL", cmfAsset.validatedAsset.principalDetail.PERPETUAL, OneHasValue(cmfAsset.validatedAsset.principalDetail.PERPETUAL));]]></expr>
        </Execute>
        <ForEach displayName="principalEvent" recordType="cmfAsset.validatedAsset.principalDetail.principalEvent">
          <Do>
            <If displayName="PRINCIPAL_EVENT_TYPE=Redemption">
              <expr><![CDATA[return Strcmp(cmfAsset.validatedAsset.principalDetail.principalEvent.PRINCIPAL_EVENT_TYPE, "Redemption");]]></expr>
              <Then>
                <Execute displayName="REDEMP_CRNCY">
                  <comment><![CDATA[ISO 3 code]]></comment>
                  <expr><![CDATA[return StoreStringIf("REDEMP_CRNCY", cmfAsset.validatedAsset.principalDetail.principalEvent.principalEventTerm.EVENT_CURRENCY, OneHasValue(cmfAsset.validatedAsset.principalDetail.principalEvent.principalEventTerm.EVENT_CURRENCY));]]></expr>
